channel.title: Website links
channel.description:
I'm not sure if it's just my computer, but in the link banner at the top of the site, the MEDIA, TEAM, and INFORMATION buttons all send me to an error page "The page you are looking for cannot be found". It has been this way since the first time I came here on launch day.
edit: Found out that the links work if you are on the homepage, but trying to click on them from here in the forums, they don't work.
